# The icedrive-sync target share starts EMPTY. The AWOW backup PUSHES selected
# archive sets here (HOMELAB_TOPOLOGY.md step 5); IceDrive's native app (on the
# real Windows box) then syncs this folder to the cloud. In the sim it is just a
# writable Samba share the backup runner pushes into. Keep this file so git
# tracks the otherwise-empty directory.
